===[[Season 1]]===
[[Illyrio Mopatis]] gives [[Daenerys Targaryen]] a wedding gift of three dragon eggs, said to be from the Shadow Lands beyond Asshai.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Winter is Coming]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

Ser [[Jorah Mormont]] tells Daenerys that in the Shadow Lands beyond Asshai there is a form of &quot;[[ghost grass]]&quot; which the [[Dothraki]] believe will one day swallow all the world.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The Kingsroad]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

Ser Jorah suggests to Daenerys that they flee Khal [[Drogo]]'s ''[[khalasar]]'' by night so as not to be caught up in the chaos unleashed when he dies. He says there is a port in Asshai they can head to;Â Daenerys refuses.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Baelor]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

===[[Season 2]]===

[[Melisandre]], a Red Priestess of the [[Lord of Light]] from Asshai, has converted [[Stannis Baratheon]] and most of his [[House Baratheon of Dragonstone|household]] to her religion and become one of his closest advisers.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The North Remembers]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

At [[Qarth]], [[Jorah Mormont]] encounters the mysterious woman [[Quaithe]], a shadowbinder from Asshai.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The Ghost of Harrenhal]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
